N2  - This paper presents an approach to the following problem involving uncertainty: the choice of sample design for the estimation of parameters which are not identified prior to the sample selection. More specificly, the author suggests the use of ?contingency planning? as developed in the realm of military systems analysis, to supplement the use of standard sample survey theory.
